  <entry>
    <title>Union-Find</title>
    <url>/2021/09/09/Union-Find/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="what-is-union-find-problem">What is Union-Find Problem</h1>
<h2 id="connectivity">Connectivity</h2>
<p><span class="math inline">\(a-b\)</span>: <span class="math inline">\(a\)</span> is connected with <span class="math inline">\(b\)</span></p>
<p>Properties:</p>
<ul>
<li><p><span class="math inline">\(a-a\)</span></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math inline">\(a-b \Longrightarrow b-a\)</span></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math inline">\(a-b,b-c \Longrightarrow a-c\)</span></p></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="connected-component">Connected Component</h2>
<p>A is a <code>connected component</code>: <span class="math inline">\(a\in{A},b\in{A} \iff a-b\)</span></p>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/connected-component.png" class="" title="3 Connected Components">
<h2 id="union-find">Union-Find</h2>
<p><span class="math inline">\(union(a,b)\)</span>: <code>connect</code> <span class="math inline">\(a\)</span> and <span class="math inline">\(b\)</span></p>
<p><span class="math inline">\(find(a,b)\)</span>: <code>check</code> if <span class="math inline">\(a\)</span> and <span class="math inline">\(b\)</span> are connected <em>(True/False)</em></p>
<p><strong><em>Problem</em></strong>:</p>
<ol type="1">
<li><p><span class="math inline">\(union()\)</span> any <span class="math inline">\(N\)</span> objects <span class="math inline">\((N\to\infty)\)</span>, at any time</p></li>
<li><p><span class="math inline">\({\forall}a,b,find(a,b)\)</span> at any time</p></li>
</ol>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/union-find-problem.png" class="" width="250" height="462" title="Example">
<h1 id="algorithms">Algorithms</h1>
<h2 id="quick-find">Quick Find</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>connected <span class="math inline">\(\Longleftrightarrow\)</span> same <strong>status</strong></p>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/quick-find.png" class="" width="584" height="300" title="Quick Find">
</blockquote>
<div class="tabs" id="quick-find"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a href="#quick-find-1">Data Structure</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#quick-find-2">union(a,b)</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#quick-find-3">find(a,b)</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="quick-find-1"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">arr[N];  // status of objects</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="tab-pane" id="quick-find-2"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sa = arr[a];  // sataus of a</span><br><span class="line">sb = arr[b];</span><br><span class="line">foreach i in arr[]:</span><br><span class="line">	if (arr[i] == sa):  // every i connected with a</span><br><span class="line">		arr[i] = sb;  // connect i to b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="tab-pane" id="quick-find-3"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">return arr[a] == arr[b];  // same status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div>
<h2 id="quick-union">Quick Union</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>A <code>connected component</code> is a <code>tree</code></p>
<p>connected <span class="math inline">\(\Longleftrightarrow\)</span> same <strong>root</strong></p>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/quick-union.png" class="" width="600" height="400" title="Quick Union">
</blockquote>
<div class="tabs" id="quick-union"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a href="#quick-union-1">Data Structure</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#quick-union-2">root(i)</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#quick-union-3">union(a,b)</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#quick-union-4">find(a,b)</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="quick-union-1"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">arr[N];  // parents of objects</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="tab-pane" id="quick-union-2"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while (i != arr[i]):  // not root</span><br><span class="line">	i = arr[i];  // go check parent</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="tab-pane" id="quick-union-3"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ra = root(a);</span><br><span class="line">rb = root(b);</span><br><span class="line">arr[ra] = rb;  // set rb as ra&#x27;s parent</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="tab-pane" id="quick-union-4"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">return root(a) == root(b);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div>
<h3 id="improvements-to-qu">Improvements to QU</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>Avoid <strong><code>Tall</code></strong> trees</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="weighted-qu">Weighted QU</h4>
<blockquote>
<p>smaller tree goes to bigger tree</p>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/weighted-qu.png" class="" title="Weighted Quick-Union">
</blockquote>
<div class="tabs" id="weighted-qu"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a href="#weighted-qu-1">Data Structure</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#weighted-qu-2">union(a,b)</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="weighted-qu-1"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">arr[N];  // parents</span><br><span class="line">size[N];  // size of each tree whose root is i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/path-compression-1.png" class="" width="300" height="375" title="size[9] &#x3D; 3, size[3] &#x3D; 8"></p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="weighted-qu-2"><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ra = root(a);</span><br><span class="line">rb = root(b);</span><br><span class="line">if (ra == rb): return;  // same root -&gt; connected -&gt; do nothing</span><br><span class="line">if (size[ra] &gt;= size[rb]):  // a&#x27;s tree is bigger</span><br><span class="line">	arr[rb] = ra;</span><br><span class="line">	size[ra] += size[rb];</span><br><span class="line">else:  // b&#x27;s tree is bigger</span><br><span class="line">	arr[ra] = rb;</span><br><span class="line">	size[rb] += size[ra];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/weighted-is-flat.png" class="" width="750" height="434" title="Weighted QU tree is flat">
<h4 id="path-compression">Path Compression</h4>
<ol type="1">
<li><p><span class="math inline">\(root(a)\)</span></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math inline">\(\forall p\ (on\ a&#39;s\ path\ to\ root): reconnect\ to\ root\)</span></p></li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/path-compression-1.png" class="" width="350" height="430" title="before">
<img src="/2021/09/09/Union-Find/path-compression-2.png" class="" width="600" height="300" title="after">
</blockquote>
<p>Weighted Quick-Union + Pass Compression: nearly <code>Linear-time</code></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Union-Find: No Linear-time algorithm</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Algorithms</category>
      </categories>
